To build you need the Java SDK 5 available from http://java.sun.com. JDK 6 is also expected to work but has not been tested.
You also need Maven2. This has been tested with Maven 2.0.4, but is also expected to work with Maven 2.0.6. Maven2 can be downloaded from http://maven.apache.org

To build run 'mvn package' from within the root directory.

Apache Tomcat 5.5.23 is recommended as a JSP container for running this application. Apache Tomcat is available from http://apache.tomcat.org


Installation, configuration and usage details can be found in docs/guide.html
